quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  12,87,"Ben ma…ď…ďe maakani …ďe: Ko onon yo …ďi…ó…ďe am, yehee tefoyon fii Yuusufa e mi√Īan-mun. Wata on ta∆īo e ko Alla yurmetee kon jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Ko fii, ta∆īotaako e yurmeende Alla nden si wanaa yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďen; tawde ko …ďe majjaa…ďe kattal Alla mawngal ngal, e …ďural Makko suu…óiingal e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  12,88,"∆Āe wa…ói ko …ďen ma…ď…ďe yamiri …ďe kon, …ďe yehi …óa…ď…ďitugol Yuusufa e mi√Īan-mun. Nde …ďe naatunoo ka Yuusufa, …ďe wi'ani mo: Tammpere e baasal he…ďii men. Men ardii e sil'a jaasu…óo fan…óu…óo. Etan-men ko timmi, wano etiranayno-…óaa men aranun, sakko-…óaa e amen ko …ďeydii kon e …óum maa sulfiraneede si'la amen fan…óu…óo on. Pellet, Alla yo…ďitiray sakko- too…ďe …ďen ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e njo…ďdi."
  12,89,"Nde o nanunoo haala ma…ď…ďe kan, o yurmaa …ďe, o anndintinori e ma…ď…ďe wiide …ďe: Hara on annditii ko wa…óuno…óon Yuusufa e neene-gooto makko on fewndo wonuno…óon majju…ďe e battane kuu…óe mon …óen e ma…ď…ďe?"
  12,90,"∆Āe Ňčal…ói, …ďe wi'i: Kere ko an woni Yuusufa? Yuusufu maakani …ďe: Eyyo, ko min woni Yuusufa. Oo mo suti…óon …óoo takko am, ko neene-gooto am. Gom…óii Alla mo∆ī∆īorike e amen …ďoortugol e ko men na…ďidi e mun, O …ďamta fii amen. Ko fii, kala hulir…óo Alla …óoftagol yamirooje Makko …óen, wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, o mu√Ī√Īii jarrabuyee, pellet, golle makko …óen e mo∆ī∆īere jeyaa. Alla non yeebataa njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen, ko O reenoowo …ďe ndi."
  12,91,"Musi…ó…ďe makko …ďen wi'ani mo hi…ďe ngantinoo e kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe: Men woondirii Alla, Alla …ďurnirii ma e amen ye…óugol ma jikkuuji timmu…ói. Pellet, men woniino e kon ko men wa…óu-maa, ko men bonnu…ďe e maa…óa too√Īu…ďe ma."
  12,92,"Yuusufu ja…ďani …ďe ngaŇčto, o maaki: Feloore alaa e hoore-mon hannde. On feletaake on Ňči√Īetaake. Yo Alla yaafano on. Ko Kanko woni Mo∆ī∆īoo Yurmetee…óo."
  12,93,"Nde o humpitinoo ko he…ďi ben makko kon e wumugol, o jonni …ďe dolokke makko on, o maaki: Yahdee e oo dolokke am …óoo, bugo…óon mo ka yeeso baaben am, …ďe wattay yi'ude. Addanon lam …ďeynguure mon nden …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe."
  12,94,"Nde lappol setee…ďe …ďen yaltunoo Misra, …ďe wo…ó…ótii saare nden, Annabi Yaaquuba maakani …ďi…ó…ďe makko …ďen e won…ďe ka leydi makko …ďen: Min mi…óo he…ďa balangol Yuusufa, sinno wanaa fii yo …óaytinam, w'ion mi…óo wowla ko mi anndaa."
  12,95,"∆Āi…ó…ďe makko wonunoo…ďe …óon …ďen wi'i: Men woondirii Alla, an on a seeraali e majjere maa …ďooyunde nden e fii Yuusufa wonnde hino hasii ka yiitaa mo."